options: ["Alice's phone number is 568-2679.", "Cindy's jacket is purple.", "The writer's   first name is Cindy.", 'Alice and Cindy are in the same  school.']
questions: Which of the following is TRUE  ?
article: Good afternoon! I'm Alice. My last name is Smith. I'm in a red jacket. I'm in Xingfu Middle School. My phone number is 569-2679. This is Cindy Brown. She is my good friend. She is in a yellow jacket. She is in Xingfu Middle School, too. What's her phone number? It's 865-2397.
